    <abstract>
      <para>
  Multiple water types (river, lagoon, ocean) from the North Slope of
  Alaska and nearshore Beaufort Sea were sampled seasonally to
  investigate biogeochemical linkages between terrestrial, lagoon, and
  open ocean ecosystems. Water samples were collected in April, June,
  July, and August and analyzed for dissolved organic carbon and total
  dissolved nitrogen content.
</para>
